                        databases, web pages, social media, etc.
                    </b>, to provide insights and recommendations for business
                    performance improvement. BI systems supported data-driven decision making and innovation. This was
                    also
                    the era when cloud computing technologies enabled scalable and flexible IT services on demand
                </p>
            </div>
